Package: community.variability
Title: Community Variability Metrics for IFCB Metacommunities
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Huy Anh", "Pham", email = "huy.pham@whoi.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates aggregate and compositional variability metrics for
    metacommunity arrays X[t, i, j], where t is time, i is site, and j is
    taxon.
